channel.description:
# Big Brother *The hit show, but on discord and the forums!* # How it works -I will post annoucements, comps, and PoV drawing, and evictions on this Thread. House chat, Jury House, and le social game will be on a discord server, it’s easiest to keep track of for me and y’all. Diary Rooms will also be on that server. -A cycle in a nutshell HoH Comp Nominiations PoV Drawings PoV Comp Veto ceremony Renom if nesscary Eviction # Terms Explained! HoH-The Head of House! Selects two people to be nominated, selects the renom, only votes in a tie. PoV-Power of Veto, can take one of the nominees off the block. Nominee-Selected by HoH, can be vetoed, can be evicted if remaining on the block post-veto cermony Backdoor-???(I know what it is, its just for you to figure out)
# Rules 1. NO ALTS LMAO 2. If you fail to vote/submit for a comp by the deadline, you get a strike, 3 and you get expelled from the house 3. follow the forum rules lmao k
# Player list 1. PoisonedSquid 2. ~~HTM~~ 3. Gamerpoke 4. Insanity 5. Mathblade 6. BlueStorm 7. ~~Pug~~ 8. OTB 9. CheesyKnives 10. ~~Hj~~ 11. Marl 12. Maxi 13. 14. 15. 16. 17. (optional) 18. (optional) # Always remember... ![etU|500x281](upload://hXXRRrbGgJ3xRo9kiEe2zMJAcj0.gif)

item.title: Big Brother [Canned Due To Fucking Inactives]
item.dc:creator: MathBlade
item.description:
You won’t get a strike because there is no active game you’re required to participate in right now

Each “day” (borrowing a mafia term) is set up into the following phases

  1. HoH Competition
  2. HoH nominates two people (or in my case I had to do three) for eviction. Eviction is BB’s “lynch”
  3. Then the HoH, the nominees, and 1-2 others (random or player specified) play in the power of Veto.
    The Power Of Veto is the King’s Pardon. If received it has to be used that day and the current HoH puts someone else up.
  4. Eviction You vote for who you want of the people nominated to go “home” or “be lynched”.

We finished step four where Htm and Pug were evicted.

We are waiting on Noz to post the next HoH challenge.
